        Generates a JCoFunction's XML schema using its metadata. Generated XML schema can be used by other applications to prepare valid XML function calls or to define metadata types within mule applications.
        Parameters:
        connection - The connection
        functionName - The name of the Function to generate its XML Schema
        encoding - Overrides default encoding defined in configuration
        disableFunctionsCache - Overrides default disable jCoFunction cache flag in configuration
        Returns:
        the functions's XML schema
